com.serotonin.mango.rt.dataImage

Class AnnotatedPointValueTime

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.serotonin.mango.rt.dataImage.PointValueTime
      • com.serotonin.mango.rt.dataImage.AnnotatedPointValueTime
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.serotonin.json.JsonSerializable, IValueTime, java.io.Serializable

    public class AnnotatedPointValueTime
extends PointValueTime
    This class provides a way of arbitrarily annotating a PointValue. Point value annotations should not be confused with Java annotations. A point value annotation will typically explain the source of the value when it did not simply come from data source.
    Author:
    Matthew Lohbihler
    See Also:
    SetPointSource, Serialized Form
